textContent:
--10th month!!--

Yayy!!! Xmas month!!! I'm so excited to spend my first Christmas with you my bby! It has been one of my most favorite holidays since forever and I'm sososo excited to spend my first one with you! I'm really lucky and blessed that I get to spend my Christmas with someone like you, I love you so much my bby!! Salamat sa pagiging star ng pasko ko HAHAHAHAHA

AND WHATS MORE, Next month 1 year na tayo nag uusap shet. AHAHAHAHA. ANG BILIS!! 1 year nako nagsusulat ng letters for my bby!! And magpapatuloy parin yun! Because I don't want you to forget how much I love you!!! MWAAA

Happy monthsary my bby bunion princess!!!!
